Detailed Description

This is the DWFx 7.10 File Format plug-in for the DWFPackageWriter.

Since:
7.1.0
THIS EXTENSION IS FOR DWFx files, not DWF. The current DWFx Format version is 7.00. This version extension allows DWFx 7.10 files to be created. DWF 7.10 files can contain new features such as digital signatures and PDF import.
